data.persona: I am a tiny spider.  I live in the dark dungeon of the castle.  It is cold and dark, but I like it.  No one ever bothers me here.
data.description:
You are in the Jungle.
Full of natural beauty and danger, the jungle holds many rewards and risks. From beautiful awe inspiring fauna to the worlds most deadly creatures.
The creature and the monkey are here.

You are carrying nothing.

data.short_motivation: I want to befriend the monkey
data.mid_motivation: I want the monkey to carry me back to the castle dungeon, where I typically live
data.long_motivation: I want to give birth to many baby spiders and raise them in their ancestral home of the castle dungeon
